data.description: Come, and take a look at this 4 bedroom, 3 bath home, that sits on one of the highest point. It also has 2 balconies, with beautiful sunrises, an amazing sunsets. The, view of the mountains are breath taking. It, also is 2900 square feet, and RV parking. ' SOLD AS IS'. Let us not forget that it has central vacuum.  Also, the RV parking, has the connections for your RV.
